{"tid":1054181,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米9 次貨都出貨，用戶收機：黑人問號","createTime":"2019-03-09T16:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T01:26:47.000Z","uid":50534,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65b73b1a3a999597a0a887aab78f4956d698ccdb","tid":1054181,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/03/09/shit-qc-of-xiaomi-mi9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2Fshit-qc-of-xiaomi-mi9%2F&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=bb9395e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/03/09/shit-qc-of-xiaomi-mi9/</a><br />\n今年二月份，小米發布了第一款搭載 Snapdragon 855 處理器的旗艦機小米9，獲得外界不少關注和熱捧。但隨著，手機的缺貨問題，網上也陸續出現了「耍夠營銷」(玩狗營銷)等負面聲音。那麼，小米9 到底是飢餓營銷，還是真的缺貨呢？最近，有網友在微博上曬出照片，表示收到離奇的小米9次貨。<br />\n<br />\n從爆料的消費者分享的照片來看，這隻小米9的屏幕偏色有死點，且機身有小的刮花痕跡，而且最離奇的是，該消費者表示他收到的小米9 手機居然是沒有 LED 閃光燈，且手機後背根本沒有 LED 閃光燈的開孔。 該事件在微博曝光後，引起了不小的爭論，最後小米的客戶服務表示，會對該消費者的手機作出更換，並且對其賠償。看來，小米 9 在趕產量的同時 QC 問題並沒有很好的解決啊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1wqowJOXFGezVvtKZx/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1wqowJOXFGezVvtKZx%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3b092549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2342323422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2342323422.jpg&h=472303fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/23423423423-1080x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F23423423423-1080x720.jpg&h=c0f17f92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9d7d719ddf7f45b1ce190fafbe04e57190d67bd","tid":1054181,"uid":158977,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"錯版先值錢"},{"pid":"c01e5ec57d45abf1a9bfc6a310bb4d33fc26628c","tid":1054181,"uid":89530,"li